===Etymology===
{{ja-kanjitab-top}}
! [[六]] || [[ヶ]] || [[月]]
{{ja-kanjitab-bottom}}
[[六]] (ろく, ''roku'') "six" + [[ヶ]] ([[箇]], か, ''ka''), the counter for months + [[月]] (げつ, ''getsu'') "month"

===Noun===
'''六ヶ月''' ([[ろっかげつ]], ''rokkagetsu'')

# [[六箇月]]: six months (duration)

